videos.headline: Ohio State strikes first vs. Michigan
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins hits Chris Olave over the middle and he sprints 24 yards to the end zone on Ohio State's opening drive vs. Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Ohio State strikes first vs. Michigan) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State defender knocks away would-be Michigan TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson scrambles and throws to Zach Gentry in the end zone, but an Ohio State defender knocks it away on third down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State defender knocks away would-be Michigan TD) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haskins' 2nd TD pass extends Buckeyes' lead
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins finds Chris Olave for their second touchdown connection of the game as Ohio State leads Michigan 14-6 in the 2nd quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Haskins' 2nd TD pass extends Buckeyes' lead) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haskins hits wide-open WR for 3rd TD pass
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins finds Johnnie Dixon all alone for a 31-yard touchdown to put Ohio State ahead 21-6 over Michigan near the end of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Haskins hits wide-open WR for 3rd TD pass) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's Collins catches off-balanced TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson throws a pass up to Nico Collins, who turns and hauls in a 23-yard touchdown to narrow Michigan's deficit vs. Ohio State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan's Collins catches off-balanced TD) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buckeyes muff kickoff and Wolverines capitalize
videos.description: Michigan recovers a muffed kickoff and immediately scores a touchdown, its second in a 6-second span, to cut its deficit to just 2.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buckeyes muff kickoff and Wolverines capitalize) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Potential Ohio State TD ruled incomplete before half
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws to Binjimen Victor near the pylon, but the pass is ruled incomplete with seconds remaining in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Potential Ohio State TD ruled incomplete before half) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State nearly squanders lead in eventful first half
videos.description: The Buckeyes lead Michigan 24-19 in a first half where they piled up 278 total yards against the Wolverines' vaunted defense.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ohio State nearly squanders lead in eventful first half) 2018/11/24 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Meyer flagged for unsportsmanlike conduct after hit on Haskins
videos.description: A Michigan defender hits Dwayne Haskins as he slides, then Urban Meyer is called for unsportsmanlike conduct on the sideline in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Meyer flagged for unsportsmanlike conduct after hit on Haskins) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bush leaves game with apparent leg injury
videos.description: Michigan linebacker Devin Bush leaves the game with an apparent leg injury after trying to make a tackle in the third quarter vs. Ohio State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bush leaves game with apparent leg injury) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Patterson's INT leads to Ohio State TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson's pass is picked off by Jordan Fuller, then Mike Weber runs in a short touchdown to pad Ohio State's lead over Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patterson’s INT leads to Ohio State TD) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Collins comes down with great TD catch
videos.description: Nico Collins comes down with the great two-handed touchdown grab as Michigan shortens its deficit vs. Ohio State in the fourth.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Collins comes down with great TD catch) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Campbell's 78-yard TD run is OSU's longest ever vs. Michigan
videos.description: Parris Campbell bounces a jet sweep outside and outraces Michigan's defense 78 yards to the end zone in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Campbell's 78-yard TD run is OSU's longest ever vs. Michigan) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Long Michigan drive ends with TD run
videos.description: Michigan fullback Ben Mason finishes a 91-yard drive with a short touchdown run as the Wolverines try to cut into Ohio State's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Long Michigan drive ends with TD run) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State eclipses 50 with short TD pass
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins' fourth touchdown pass puts Ohio State up 55-32 vs. Michigan - the most points the Buckeyes have ever scored in the rivalry.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State eclipses 50 with short TD pass) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State INT leads to Haskins' 5th TD pass
videos.description: Brendon White intercepts Michigan backup quarterback Joe Milton, then Dwayne Haskins throws to Parris Campbell for his fifth touchdown pass.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State INT leads to Haskins' 5th TD pass) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan backup QB scores 1st career TD
videos.description: Michigan freshman quarterback Joe Milton keeps it himself on the read option and beats Ohio State to the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan backup QB scores 1st career TD) 2018/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haskins' 5 TDs power Ohio State's 62-39 rout over Michigan
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws five touchdown passes as Ohio State puts up 62 points vs. Michigan, the most ever against a Jim Harbaugh-coached team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Haskins' 5 TDs power Ohio State's 62-39 rout over Michigan) 2018/11/24 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: What is Jim Harbaugh's future at Michigan?
videos.description: After Michigan's disappointing loss to Ohio State, Paul Finebaum and Jonathan Vilma question if it's time for a change in Ann Arbor.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (What is Jim Harbaugh’s future at Michigan?) 2018/11/25 ESHEET SC
